com.intuit.wasabi.tests.model

Class Experiment

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intuit.wasabi.tests.model.ModelItem
      • com.intuit.wasabi.tests.model.Experiment

  • public class Experiment
extends ModelItem
    A simplified Experiment class which can be instantiated in various ways and modified directly via methods or public access to make it easy to test around with it.

      • Experiment

        public Experiment(String label,
                  Application application,
                  String startTime,
                  String endTime,

                  String description,
                  String rule,
                  Boolean isPersonalizationEnabled,
                  String modelName,
                  String modelVersion,
                  Boolean isRapidExperiment,
                  Integer userCap,
                  String creatorID)
        Creates an experiment.
        Parameters:
        label - the experiment label (will be prefixed)
        application - the application name (will be prefixed)
        startTime - the start time
        endTime - the end time
        samplingPercent - the sampling percentage (0, 1]
        description - the experiment description
        rule - a rule set for the experiment
        isPersonalizationEnabled - flag for personalization
        modelName - the model name
        modelVersion - the model version
        isRapidExperiment - flag if rapid experimentation
        userCap - max users for rapid experiments
        creatorID - the creator
